00:50:22,807 --> 00:50:24,798
- Get him out of here!
- Where's my nephew, huh?

704
00:50:24,976 --> 00:50:26,910
- Come on, get him off.
- Where is he?

705
00:50:27,078 --> 00:50:28,807
- Come on!
- You mother...

