744
00:52:20,791 --> 00:52:22,759
I said, go home.
Let me handle it, okay?

745
00:52:22,927 --> 00:52:24,189
Lorenzo.

746
00:52:24,462 --> 00:52:26,862
I don't know who
you think you are...

747
00:52:27,031 --> 00:52:29,591
