Gets you off the hook.

751
00:53:20,952 --> 00:53:23,716
No. No, no. No.

752
00:53:23,888 --> 00:53:27,187
Come on. The kid's dead.
She did it. I mean, fuck her.

753
00:53:27,358 --> 00:53:30,794
