Karen doesn't wear bug bands.

863
01:01:56,500 --> 01:01:59,901
Jesus. Anything bit Karen,
it'd lose its mind.

864
01:02:00,070 --> 01:02:01,731
Really? Why?

865
01:02:01,905 --> 01:02:04,874
Because Karen's son was abducted.

866
01:02:05,275 --> 01:02:07,106
Our first kid.

867
01:02:07,644 --> 01:02:09,202
You mean, Kent?

868
01:02:09,746 --> 01:02:11,680
Ten years ago.

869
01:02:13,851 --> 01:02:15,876
Tina here was a baby.

870
01:02:16,520 --> 01:02:19,318
We all knew each other
from the neighborhood.

871
01:02:19,490 --> 01:02:21,515
- Karen got us together.
- Cody Martin!

872
01:02:21,692 --> 01:02:24,490
We had no idea what the hell
we were doing...

873
01:02:24,661 --> 01:02:28,620
...but we wound up combing
every goddamn forest...

874
01:02:28,799 --> 01:02:34,499
...field, drainpipe, creek, culvert...
Oh, everywhere.

875
01:02:35,539 --> 01:02:39,475
And you know, we...
We still post flyers.

876
01:02:40,677 --> 01:02:43,271
Well, what can I say? We...

877
01:02:43,447 --> 01:02:46,245
We got better at it with practice.

878
01:02:47,351 --> 01:02:50,548
Karen knows who took him too.
The cops just can't prove it.

879
01:02:50,721 --> 01:02:52,313
- We can't prove it.
- Yeah.

880
01:02:52,489 --> 01:02:53,922
God.

881
01:02:54,091 --> 01:02:56,685
Me and Kent went to school together.
So like...

882
01:02:56,860 --> 01:02:59,055
...I know he's my own age and all.

883
01:02:59,229 --> 01:03:02,027
When we find him, I'm still
expecting him to be 8 years old...

884
01:03:02,199 --> 01:03:03,666
...like the last time I saw him.

885
01:03:04,701 --> 01:03:06,259
Cody!

886
01:03:08,138 --> 01:03:10,003
- Cody!
- Come on, Cody!

887
01:03:12,142 --> 01:03:13,871
So why you all triple-teaming me...

888
01:03:14,044 --> 01:03:16,569
...while Karen's got Brenda
by herself all up in her ear?

