- Sympathy.

891
01:03:20,817 --> 01:03:24,583
I never lost a child, Lorenzo.
Did you?

892
01:03:36,767 --> 01:03:39,065
- Cody!
- Cody Martin!

893
01:03:40,404 --> 01:03:42,599
Hey, Cody!

894
01:03:43,273 --> 01:03:45,207
Cody Martin!

895
01:03:46,910 --> 01:03:48,935
